        <Parent_String>calcium carbonate white pigment [300218052], transparent white pigment [300013779], white pigment [300013723], pigment by color [300013134], pigments [300013109], colorant (material) [300013026], materials by function [300014692], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
